    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have opened up the floodgates to new multi-tools with your innovations. You can build as many multi-tools as you please, but instead of starting with 6 TP like your original did, your additional multi-tools only start with 4 TP, and are treated as martial weapons (gaining 2 TP instead of the 4 TP of the advanced primary multi-tool). Additionally, you add the resonant trait (worth 2 TP) and the injection trait (worth 3 TP) to the list of traits you can use when creating melee multi-tools, and you add the propulsive trait (worth 1 TP) to the list of traits you can use when creating ranged multi-tools.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If your invention is a skysteel multi-tool, you immediately gain your second multi-tool, and it starts with 6 TP, and then any additional multi-tools start with just 4 TP. You cannot add your modifications to these tools, but you can use any unlocked traits when building them.</p>",
